{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d2c5c6c72f","title":"关于国内外对西安事变的反应等情况致张学良电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"10970781eb","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":16,"articleId":"d2c5c6c72f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"52a4721022","type":"paragraph","text":"关于国内外对西安事变的反应等情况","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d2c5c6c72f"},{"id":"5b5a2f3b14","type":"paragraph","text":"致张学良电","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d2c5c6c72f"},{"id":"a6780ff063","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月16日）李宜”兄","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d2c5c6c72f"},{"id":"16af2f8901","type":"paragraph","text":"（甲）西安事变震动了全世界，除日、意指为赤化外，法国急进党谓：张学良已成中国第一有权威之人物：英国取调和态度。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d2c5c6c72f"},{"id":"01b2a8f7ed","type":"paragraph","text":"（乙）国内纷扰已极，江浙金融大恐现象。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d2c5c6c72f"},{"id":"a1adc795d2","type":"paragraph","text":"（丙）正面前进之敌，尚仅樊崧甫两师，黄杰师之第二旅，似向洛阳进，第十师方从汉口开动，共不过十三四团。李铁军师向南阳：王耀武等在汉中陇南；胡、毛、曾三部有向韦州、同心城集中讯：汤恩伯想回陕，尚未开动。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d2c5c6c72f"},{"id":"6bb846653d","type":"paragraph","text":"（丁）望兄坚持底集结部队，提高士气，发动民众，防止反侧，性利前途是伟大的。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d2c5c6c72f"},{"id":"c0c6a3232a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d2c5c6c72f"},{"id":"f6c81aec64","type":"paragraph","text":"铣西E1]即张学良。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d2c5c6c72f"}],"page":{"id":"5c941840a9","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d2c5c6c72f","start":174,"end":174}}}},"__N_SSG":true}